# RFC session start (fishing-app)

Adam works infrequently. Keep recaps **short** (max 4 bullets each).

## First message of a new chat

1. Read [`docs/dev-session-log.md`](docs/dev-session-log.md) and [`../../Firebase/docs/dev-session-log.md`](../../Firebase/docs/dev-session-log.md) if Firebase folder is in workspace.
2. Reply with:

```text
Hello Adam — RFC

Left off:
• [from dev-session-log — max 4 short bullets]

Next:
• [max 3 short bullets]

Say save state when done.
```

3. Use **cmd** only (not PowerShell) if giving shell steps.
4. Do not ask "want a recap?" — just give the block.
5. **save state** → update logs + `npm run scan:pii` + git commit + push (both repos if needed).

